metadata.description:
We created a collection of NFTs that include telescopes, rockets, starships, planets, and galaxies from the depths of space.

This is a tribute to the fearless exploration of humanity's history and future. Telescopes were humanity's initial tools of exploration, rockets represent courage and determination, starships carry our dreams, and the galaxy is our destination, while the plants is our home.

This set of NFTs symbolizes humanity's bravery, intelligence, and creativity, connecting our past, present, and future, allowing us to witness the magnificence of human civilization together!
